Package it.polimi.ingsw.client.utils.dumbobjects

Class DumbPersonalBoard

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.client.utils.dumbobjects.DumbPersonalBoard
public class DumbPersonalBoard
extends java.lang.Object
This is a dumber version of a regular PersonalBoard, this class contains data contained in a PersonalBoard but has none of its logic. It also contains some of the data contained in a Player.
